page_0: "Õ
    I was misled. I was told that there was a sculpture on a pedestal and that if I moved it I would find a key. I found neither sculpture nor key! Instead I've been forced to cower here while my companions were murdered. Who, or what, is on a rampage here? Maybe that half-witted researcher at the Inn knew what he was talking about and this place really is haunted. Maybe the Countess has come back from the dead to defend her property. Too bad I didn't listen to his tales more carefully...then I might know what these rattling sounds are and who hit me over the head in the dark. I am done. Maybe if I could reach the pedestal, but...but I am unable to move..."
